38:06.786 --> 38:08.955
What about Ellie do you have in you?

38:10.957 --> 38:12.375
Do you know who Ellie is?

38:13.960 --> 38:17.172
She's a girl with a broken relationship
with her mother,

38:18.173 --> 38:21.593
who never understood her
and couldn't empathize with her.

38:23.345 --> 38:25.847
Until one day, by magic,

38:27.349 --> 38:29.893
her mother starts living in Ellie's body.

38:31.019 --> 38:33.313
And Ellie in her mother's.

38:36.274 --> 38:37.984
You don't know what's happening to you.

38:39.235 --> 38:40.653
Everything is new to you.

38:43.656 --> 38:47.994
And you wonder why
this is happening to you.

38:51.081 --> 38:52.582
What do you have to discover?

39:00.215 --> 39:01.633
[piano playing]

39:04.636 --> 39:05.637
[sighs]

39:17.565 --> 39:19.818
The original version of this number
isn't like this.

39:19.901 --> 39:21.986
As an artist,
you have to adapt to changes.

39:22.862 --> 39:25.198
Now you'll see what it's like
to be the real Ellie.

39:27.158 --> 39:28.451
Caterina.

39:29.577 --> 39:31.454
[crowd murmuring]

39:45.343 --> 39:47.220
[piano playing]

40:04.904 --> 40:06.156
[piano stops playing]

40:10.785 --> 40:13.663
